<p>'Would you shut up, man?,' a visibly exasperated Biden said about 20 minutes into the debate after Trump interrupted him again as he tried to talk about the Supreme Court </p>

<p>It happened so many times that moderate Chris Wallace stepped in, asking the president to let Biden finish his answer and chided 'I'm the moderator of this debate and I would like you to let me ask my question and then you can answer,' Wallace said told Trump. 'Go ahead then,' Trump said and then later adding to Wallace: 'I guess I'm debating you, not him. No surprise' </p>

